'''''4 Play ('''yasubiwemo muri'' Nollywood nka '''''4 can Play''''' by De-Kross Movies kuko gukwirakwiza mpuzamahanga) ni filimi yasohotse muuri 2010 yakokerewe muri [[Nigeriya|Nigeria]] na  [[Gana|Ghana]] ikozwe mu bwoko bwa romantic blue comedy  yayobowe na Frank Rajah Arase, Star Majid Michel, Yvonne Okoro, John Dumelo, Jackie Appiah, Roselyn Ngissah na Juliet Ibrahim .   Filime ikurikirwa ''nuruhererekane rwiswe 4Play Reloaded'', rwasohotse muri 2011.  Yakiriye nomination 3 muri Gana Movie Awards muri 2010 kandi amaherezo yegukana igihembo cy'umukinnyi ''mwiza witwaye neza'' .  

